sequenceDiagram
  participant Seller
  participant UI as Evidence Panel
  participant API as Backend API
  participant HASH as Proof Hash Service
  participant ST as Stellar Service
  participant SC as Soroban Contract
  Seller->>UI: Upload/simulate evidence
  UI->>API: POST /submit-proof
  API->>HASH: sha256(file bytes)
  HASH-->>API: proof hash
  API->>ST: record ProofSubmitted
  ST->>SC: submit_proof_hash
  SC-->>ST: tx hash
  API-->>UI: proof hash + tx hash
